casebody.data:
Walker
v.
The N.C. State Board of Dental Examiners 95PA16-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. July 13, 2016 Ryan McKaig, Attorney at Law, Elizabeth Brooks Scherer, Attorney at Law, Raleigh, for Walker, Cynthia (D.D.S.). Carolin Bakewell, Attorney at Law, Matthew W. Sawchak, Attorney at Law, Raleigh, for The N.C. State Board Of Dental Examiners.

The following order has been entered on the Motion for Extension of Time to File Brief filed on the 12th of July 2016 by Respondent:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference, this the 13th of July 2016."

Respondent shall have up to and including the 14th day of September 2016 to file and serve his/her brief with this Court.
